        "source": "– Johanna Sainzburg, Fresh Fruit Magnate"
      }
    ],
    "adventuring": "Merchants share a certain kinship with adventurers, often hiring them over professional caravan guards. Adventurers are adaptable and enterprising by nature, making them ideal candidates for partnership in a trading company, bringing Merchants into contact with all manner of colourful characters."
